Improvements from 2.2 to 2.3
----------------------------

  1. BUG: Computer wizards refused to cast Magic Bow if they had double
     or triple in effect. Bows and swords are cumulative so it is
     desirable to cast them with triple. NOW FIXED

  2. EDITED spell descriptions: Gray Elf, Willy, Arctic Wolf, Gravity,
     Virtue (btw: why is this spell called Virtue?), Paradigm Shift,
     Ball Lightning, Emerald Dragon, Battle Cry, Coercion (shouldn't
     this be called mind blank or something?), Materialize, Meddle.

  3. BUG: Magic Glass doesn't say "Blocks LOS Enemy Only" on 2nd info
     screen.  FIXED.

  4. BUG: a dragon just shot my wizard through a magic glass. The "l"
     key shows that the dragon does not have line of sight to my wizard
     yet he shot him anyway. The shooting routine (at least for
     independents) must not be taking into account Line of Sight rules
     100%. FIXED

  5. CHANGED: Dagger -> Poison Dagger

  6. CHANGED: Basilisk ranged weapon to attack movement rating.
     (Basilisks are supposed to paralyze with their gaze according to
     the Monster Manual 8)

