 31. Allegedly completed implementation of Volcano.

 32. Added two new generators: one for birds, one for dragons.

 33. Improved the loading and saving of the probability table.

 34. FIXED at last the ReleaseSemaphore problem when quiting the game.

 35. Made fake wizards actually capable of spell casting.

 36. Allowed combat on movement rating (see Arctic Wolf).

 37. Added: Arctic Wolf, Virtue, Shadow City, Basilisk, Achiyalabopa,
     and Paradigm Shift.

 38. Made <RETURN> equivalent to end-of-turn. Problem: holding down
     return will cause multiple player to have end-of-turn. To overcome
     this I have put in a delay, but this is a rather weak solution. If
     only there was a RAWKEYUP IDCMP event this would be easy to fix,
     but I couldn't find anything in the docs about doing this.

 39. Replaced $ in chaos.font with a bullet.

 40. Improved the image for the Nuke spell.

 41. Improved the image for the Lightning spell.

 42. Added: Animate, Ball Lightning, Shocker, Basalt Golem, Emerald
     Dragon, Willy, Glass, Battle Cry, Coercion, Confidence, Eye for an
     Eye, Torment, and Materialize.

 43. Made the secret powerup GreenDragon->EmeraldDragon.

 44. Implemented Eye-for-an-Eye in combat routines.

 45. Fixed a small problem in the intro sequence where "Wizards" and
